Steps to compile the 1/4-degree HYCOM:

1. cd /scratch2/portfolios/NCEPDEV/marine/save/Your_first_name.Your_latst_name/hycom/GLBa0.24/src_2.2.35_32_mpi

2. Get necessary modules:
module remove pgi
module add intel
module add intel mpt

3. Remove old files:
rm -f *.o
rm -f *mod
rm Make.log
rm Make_log_new

4. Compile the code:
csh Make.com > & Make.log

5. Check Make.log to make sure there are no problems.
